            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1206308</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Tesla Cybertruck 将于下周 11 月 30 日正式交付，刚好是该原型车首次公开亮相的四年后。Tesla 将于下周四开始向客户交付其首款电动卡车，并有望宣布诸如电池和驱动系统规格、性能和续航数据以及价格等细节。</p><p>发布前，已有关于 Cybertruck 的新照片和影片由小红书用户发布，并持续在线上流传，展示了白色饰板版本，包括触摸屏用户界面（UI）、方形方向盘、巨大的中控台、运动座椅和玻璃车顶等。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1206341 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTbXYAATQVv-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTbXYAATQVv-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTbXYAATQVv-675x900.jpeg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTbXYAATQVv-768x1024.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTbXYAATQVv-1152x1536.jpeg 1152w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTbXYAATQVv.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲网上流传图片</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1206344 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTcWQAAwEtz-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTcWQAAwEtz-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTcWQAAwEtz-675x900.jpeg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTcWQAAwEtz-768x1024.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTcWQAAwEtz-1152x1536.jpeg 1152w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTcWQAAwEtz.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" />▲其中一张照片拍摄了触摸萤幕的显示器，揭示了部分菜单。可看到后盖（开/关）、悬挂设置（进入/低/高）、方向盘和后视镜调节、头灯、儿童锁、窗口锁、哨兵模式、洗车模式等控制项。（网上流传图片）</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1206347 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTYW4AAIMOI-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTYW4AAIMOI-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTYW4AAIMOI-675x900.jpeg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTYW4AAIMOI-768x1024.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTYW4AAIMOI-1152x1536.jpeg 1152w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTYW4AAIMOI.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲前座椅拥有侧向支撑和穿孔材料，可见其配备了通风和加热功能。（网上流传图片）</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1206350 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTbXQAAWcG5-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTbXQAAWcG5-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTbXQAAWcG5-675x900.jpeg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTbXQAAWcG5-768x1024.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTbXQAAWcG5-1152x1536.jpeg 1152w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTbXQAAWcG5.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲带盖子打开的前行李箱的照片，显示出其容量。（网上流传图片）</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1206354 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkQWYXMAAADrx-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkQWYXMAAADrx-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkQWYXMAAADrx-675x900.jpeg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkQWYXMAAADrx-768x1024.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkQWYXMAAADrx-1152x1536.jpeg 1152w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkQWYXMAAADrx.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲三角形的侧镜盖和挡风玻璃雨刷。（网上流传图片）</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1206356 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkQWYW8AAt_dA-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkQWYW8AAt_dA-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkQWYW8AAt_dA-675x900.jpeg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkQWYW8AAt_dA-768x1024.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkQWYW8AAt_dA-1152x1536.jpeg 1152w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkQWYW8AAt_dA.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲还有一张从前方拍摄的 Cybertruck 行驶中的照片。（网上流传图片）</p><p>据了解，本周 Tesla 还在其展厅放置的广告海报上透露，Cybertruck 的牵引能力为 11,000 磅，载重为 2,500 磅。</p><p>横幅还提到，Cybertruck 的车床由超坚固的片状模塑复合材料（SMC）制成，玻璃具有抗破裂性，而且拥有超硬不锈钢外骨骼，所有这些特性共同使其成为「世界上最坚固的卡车」。</p><p>根据 Tesla 产品设计总监 Javier Verdura 的说法，届时 11 月 30 日会向客户交付首批 Cybertruck，相信会有更多关于 Cybertruck 的资讯曝光。交付活动将在德州 Gigafactory 举行，但可能只有 10 辆车会在此次活动中交付。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://insideevs.com/news/697558/tesla-cybertruck-leaked-photos-provide-best-look-yet-inside-out/">insideevs</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

